## n8n@0.216.3 View the [commits](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/compare/n8n@0.216.2...n8n@0.216.3) for this version.
**Release date:** 2023-03-09 This is a bug fix release. It reverts the `isPending` check on the user entity, resolving an issue with displaying user options when user management is disabled.
